                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-southland-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                  Host, AG & Culture Podcast
                </li>
              </ul>
              <blockquote class="mt-5 border-l-4 border-southland-green/30 pl-4 text-sm italic text-shopify-secondary-text">
                "What keeps me going is watching a grower try something different with their soil and come back a season later saying it actually worked. That's the whole reason Southland exists."
              </blockquote>
              <a
                href="/podcast/"
                class="mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-southland-green hover:underline"
              >
                <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12 1a9 9 0 00-9 9v7c0 1.66 1.34 3 3 3h3v-8H5v-2c0-3.87 3.13-7 7-7s7 3.13 7 7v2h-4v8h3c1.66 0 3-1.34 3-3v-7a9 9 0 00-9-9z"></path>
                </svg>
                Listen to the AG & Culture Podcast
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Allen Reynolds -->
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row">
            <div class="shrink-0">
              <img
                src={allenPhoto}
                alt="Allen Reynolds, VP & Director of Operations at Southland Organics"
                class="h-64 w-full object-cover sm:h-full sm:w-56"
                width="224"
                height="300"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-shopify-title">Allen Reynolds</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-southland-green">VP & Director of Operations</p>
              <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1.5 text-sm text-shopify-secondary-text">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-southland-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                  10+ years helping commercial poultry growers improve performance
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-southland-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                  Thousands of farm visits across the Southeast and beyond
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-southland-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                  Antibiotic-free poultry specialist since 2017
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-southland-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
