              </blockquote>
              <a
                href="https://www.youtube.com/@PoultryBiosecurity"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-southland-green hover:underline"
